This is an Android Library project for Drag and Drop Listviews based off the Gingerbread Music app's code.

Usage can be see in the Demo subdirectory. Examples can be found in TeslaCoil's TeslaLED (https://market.android.com/details?id=com.teslacoilsw.flashlight Settings > Configure Pages) or WidgetLocker 2.2 (https://market.android.com/details?id=com.teslacoilsw.widgetlocker  Settings > Behavior > Ringer Mode Slider)


